e is, I should note, a case before the Supreme Court right now =E2=80=94 Go=
nzalez v. Google ( https://www.supremecourt.gov/docket/docketfiles/html/pub=
lic/21-1333.html ) =E2=80=94 about whether recommendation engines are cover=
ed by Section 230.

